I&rsquo;m a flexible learner and detail oriented individual with valuable experience in different fields such as Web Developing, Deep learning, Networking&hellip;
As a boy with team work character, I always work side by side with team in all companies at which I have worked.
I extremely enjoy new experiences and challenges. In other word I prefer to follow new challenges instead of routine works. The quote &ldquo;Either try as hard as you wish or wish as hard as you try&rdquo; has been always my motto.
